  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Social Care Sector COVID-19 Support Taskforce: report on first phase of COVID-19 pandemic
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This report sets out the progress and learning from the first phase of the COVID-19 pandemic in informing advice and recommendations to government and the social care sector.</p>

  </div>
</div>

